THIS HOME IS IN THE OPEN APPLICATION PERIOD | Accessible Dwelling Unit: No<br>
<br>
Welcome to Terrace View Apartments! Close in Brooklyn neighborhood with views of Mt Hood. 2 blocks from MAX station. Great walking, biking and just a 5-minute drive to downtown.<br>
<br>
We are pleased to offer this spacious ground floor unit; it features 1 bed / 1 bath. With a large bedroom that fits king size bed, larger living room off the kitchen with big windows and plenty of light. Perks include hardwood floors, radiant heating and views of Mount hood! You'll also receive 1 off-street parking spot. Enjoy accessibility to downtown, Sellwood, and Division / Hawthorne while still living in a quiet neighborhood. You're also just two blocks to the orange line max. Up to two pets are welcome.<br>
<br>
<br>
** #4419 will be available for tours/move in by 8/26 <br>
<br>
KEY FEATURES<br>
<br>
Rent: $1345<br>
