Bedrooms: 1 Bed<br>
Bathrooms: 1 Bath<br>
Parking: Off street<br>
Lease Duration: Flex<br>
Deposit: Half Months Rent, Based on screening, no more than 1 months' Rent<br>
Pets Policy: Cats &amp; Dogs OK<br>
